title: Bulls Hot Start To The Season, Bucks Stay Motivated
description:
Brian Windhorst welcomes a new member of the ESPN family Jamal Collier to discuss what to make of the Bulls’ great start to the season, free throws being down across the league, how the Bucks are staying motivated and what next level Giannis can reach.
